    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Experience the pinnacle of automotive preservation. This masterfully maintained vehicle arrives in showroom-original condition, offering a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer who demands nothing less than perfection. From the mirror-finish exterior to the untouched interior cabin, every detail reflects a standard of care that is simply unmatched in the pre-owned market. This is not merely a used car; it is a definitive statement of quality and pride of ownership.",
      "price": 48900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
